Overview
Planet Shop is a simple HTML and CSS project designed to showcase a fictional planetary shop interface. The project focuses on the planet Mercury, providing brief information about it and displaying interactive buttons for purchasing or learning more.

This project is a visually appealing static web page that can serve as a base for more complex e-commerce or educational applications.

Features
A responsive header with navigation links.
Highlighted Sign Up button with hover effects.
Main section divided into three parts:
Left Content: Displays the planet's name.
Center Content: Describes the planet Mercury and includes action buttons.
Right Content: Displays an image of Mercury.
Modern design with stylish buttons and hover effects.
Clean and organized code using Flexbox for layout.
Technologies Used
HTML5: For structuring the webpage.
CSS3: For styling and layout.
Google Fonts: For custom font styling (Montserrat Subrayada).


Future Enhancements
Add support for more planets with additional pages.
Implement a JavaScript-powered shopping cart for users.
Include dynamic content using APIs (e.g., fetching real-time planet data).
Make the site fully responsive for smaller devices like smartphones.
